name: Blueberry #1  By The Doggies Nuts Seeds Bank
description:
Sex : Regular

 Type : Indica / Sativa, Mostly indica 

Flowering : Photoperiod Genetics : 80% indica, 20% sativa 

Flowering Time : Medium Outdoor Harvest : N/A 

Height : Medium THC Level : Medium 

Characteristics : Finest tasting herbs   


Doggies Nuts Seeds Blueberry #1 is a plant of indica stature. Genetics are 80% indica, 20% sativa.  Blueberry #1  buds grow large, dense and ooze with blueberry scented resin. Resin crystals start to form at around 3 weeks into flowering to produce one of the finest tasting herbs available. Its Cannabis Seeds are a renowned old favourite, sought after for its flavour, its aroma and its ability to leave you devastated but hungry for more. Now crossed and crossed again finally a Blueberry that is truly stable. The Original Blueberry # 1 is a mostly Indica (80% Indica, 20% Sativa) strain, that dates to the late 1970´s. A large producer under optimum conditions. Blueberry #1 is a dense and stout plant with red, purple and finally blue hues, that usually cure to a lavender blue. The finished product of Blueberry #1 has a very fruity aroma and a great taste of blueberry. 

Blueberry #1 produces a notable and pleasantly euphoric high of the highest quality and is very long-lasting. Medium to large calyxes. "Blueberry" has a long shelf life and has a flowering period of 8 - 10 weeks. It harvests outdoors between 2nd - 3rd week of October.
